title: Daz3d Hahana for Kalea7
description:
http://www.daz3d.com/hahana-for-kalea-7

Details
Hahana has one of those faces you never forget.

You are going to love rendering images with this beautiful dark skinned character that comes with a custom head morph sculpted in ZBrush and mixed with Kalea 7 and Genesis 3 Female Head Morphs.

Her beautiful skin, based on Genesis 3 Female UV maps, is enhanced with Iray and 3Delight material presets and with many make-up options.

What's Included and Features
Hahana For Kalea 7: (.DUF)
Hahana Character Preset
Hahana Head Apply/REM
Hahana Body Apply/REM
Hahana Full Apply/REM
Material Options:
Iray and 3Delight Version of Each Material Preset
01 Skin
06 Eye Colors
Eye Reflections Fake/Real 3Delight Only
07 Makeup Options
01 Natural Face
06 Lipsticks
01 Natural lips
Eyelashes Black
Eye lashes Brown
Textures Include:
23 Texture, Bump, Normal and Specular Maps (4096 x 4096)
12 Texture, Bump and transparency Maps (2048 x 2048)
This product uses the Genesis 3 Female Base Female UV Maps
Daz Studio Iray Material Presets (.DUF)
Daz Studio 3Delight Material Presets (.DUF)
Notes
This product includes:
1 DSON Core Installer
